The paper discusses optimization methods for deep learning, which is a topic that falls under several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper specifically focuses on optimization methods for neural networks. The next likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which also covers topics related to neural networks. The paper also touches on topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures (cs.DS), which are all relevant to deep learning.
